---
---
<section class="section referral">
  <div class="container referral-grid reveal">
    <div class="referral-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Programa de parceiros</p>
      <h2>Indique e ganhe</h2>
      <p>Contadores, designers e parceiros que indicam clientes para a Registrium recebem comissão por cada indicação convertida. Simples assim — sem exclusividade, sem burocracia, e sua indicação segue com o mesmo acompanhamento e transparência de sempre.</p>
      <a class="button button--primary" href="/parceiros">
        Quero indicar
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="referral-art">
      <svg class="ra-graphic" viewBox="0 0 240 240" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <defs>
          <linearGradient id="refHubGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#3e6fe6"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#8a57ce"/>
          </linearGradient>
        </defs>
        <circle class="ra-glow" cx="120" cy="120" r="70" fill="url(#refHubGrad)" opacity=".16"/>
        <path d="M120 120 46 64" stroke="#8a57ce" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="3 7" stroke-linecap="round" opacity=".5"/>
        <path d="M120 120 194 58" stroke="#3e6fe6" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="3 7" stroke-linecap="round" opacity=".5"/>
        <path d="M120 120 186 188" stroke="#f5a623" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity=".55"/>
        <circle r="4.5" fill="#ffd700">
          <animateMotion dur="2.6s" repeatCount="indefinite" path="M120 120 186 188"/>
        </circle>
        <circle cx="46" cy="64" r="21" fill="var(--color-white)" stroke="#8a57ce" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <path d="M46 58a5.5 5.5 0 100 11 5.5 5.5 0 000-11z" fill="#8a57ce"/>
        <path d="M35 76c1.8-5 5.6-7.8 11-7.8s9.2 2.8 11 7.8" stroke="#8a57ce" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <circle cx="194" cy="58" r="21" fill="var(--color-white)" stroke="#3e6fe6" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <path d="M194 52a5.5 5.5 0 100 11 5.5 5.5 0 000-11z" fill="#3e6fe6"/>
        <path d="M183 70c1.8-5 5.6-7.8 11-7.8s9.2 2.8 11 7.8" stroke="#3e6fe6" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <circle cx="186" cy="188" r="22" fill="var(--color-white)" stroke="#f5a623" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <text x="186" y="195" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Plus Jakarta Sans, sans-serif" font-weight="800" font-size="17" fill="#f5a623">%</text>
        <circle cx="120" cy="120" r="38" fill="url(#refHubGrad)"/>
      </svg>
      <img class="ra-hub-mark" src="/images/logo-mark-white.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />
      <div class="ra-badge one">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M4 12l5 5L20 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        Comissão por indicação
      </div>
      <div class="ra-badge two">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M4 12l5 5L20 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        Sem exclusividade
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-teaser">
    <div class="container">
      <h3>Ficou com alguma dúvida?</h3>
      <p>Veja as perguntas mais frequentes sobre registro de marca e taxas do INPI, ou fale direto com nossa equipe pelo WhatsApp.</p>
      <a class="button button--primary" href="/blog/duvidas-frequentes">Central de dúvidas</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
.referral { padding-bottom: 0; }
.referral-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.05fr .95fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; }
.referral-copy h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; margin: .75rem 0 1.125rem; line-height: 1.08; }
.referral-copy p { color: var(--color-muted); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.65; max-width: 30rem; margin: 0 0 1.75rem; }
.referral-art { position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 16rem; }
.ra-graphic { width: 100%; max-width: 20rem; height: auto; filter: drop-shadow(0 30px 40px rgba(90,70,210,.28)); }
.ra-glow { animation: raPulse 4s ease-in-out infinite; transform-origin: 120px 120px; }
@keyframes raPulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: .16; } 50% { transform: scale(1.12); opacity: .26; } }
.ra-hub-mark { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; width: 2.5rem; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); pointer-events: none; }
.ra-badge { position: absolute; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem; background: var(--color-white); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); color: var(--color-violet); border-radius: 999px; padding: .55rem 1rem; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700; box-shadow: 0 14px 28px -14px rgba(30,20,80,.35); white-space: nowrap; animation: badgeFloat 5s ease-in-out infinite; }
.ra-badge.one { top: 8%; right: 2%; }
.ra-badge.two { bottom: 10%; left: 0; animation-delay: 1.2s; }
@keyframes badgeFloat { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); } 50% { transform: translateY(-8px); } }
.faq-teaser { margin-top: 4.5rem; background: var(--color-cream); padding: 3.5rem 0; text-align: center; }
.faq-teaser h3 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 .875rem; }
.faq-teaser p { color: var(--color-muted); font-size: .97rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 32rem; margin: 0 auto 1.625rem; }
@media (max-width: 920px) { .referral-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; gap: 2rem; } .referral-copy p { margin-inline: auto; } .referral-art { order: -1; } }
@media (max-width: 560px) { .faq-teaser { padding: 2.75rem 0; margin-top: 3.5rem; } }
</style>
